L["CNF130"] = "There is in fact an 'I' in Norris, but there is no 'team' not even close."
L["CNF131"] = "Scotty in Star Trek often says 'Ye cannae change the laws of physics.' This is untrue. Chuck Norris can change the laws of physics. With his fists."
L["CNF132"] = "Chuck Norris doesn't stub his toes. He accidentally destroys chairs, bed frames, and sidewalks."
